README.md
     1Ôćĺ# dotenv [![NPM version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/dotenv.svg?style=flat-square)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/dotenv) [![downloads](https://img.shields.io/npm/dw/dotenv)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/dotenv)
     3Ôćĺ<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/motdotla/dotenv/master/dotenv.svg" alt="dotenv" align="right" width="200" />
     4Ôćĺ
     5ÔćĺDotenv is a zero-dependency module that loads environment variables from a `.env` file into [`process.env`](https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/process.html#process_process_env). Storing configuration in the environment separate from code is based on [The Twelve-Factor App](https://12factor.net/config) methodology.
     6Ôćĺ
     7Ôćĺ[Watch the tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YtkZR0NFd1g)
     8Ôćĺ
     9Ôćĺ&nbsp;
    10Ôćĺ
    11Ôćĺ## Usage
    13ÔćĺInstall it.
    14Ôćĺ
    15Ôćĺ```sh
    16Ôćĺnpm install dotenv --save
    17Ôćĺ```
    18Ôćĺ
    19ÔćĺCreate a `.env` file in the root of your project:
    20Ôćĺ
    21Ôćĺ```ini
    22Ôćĺ# .env
    23ÔćĺS3_BUCKET="YOURS3BUCKET"
    24ÔćĺSECRET_KEY="YOURSECRETKEYGOESHERE"
    25Ôćĺ```
    26Ôćĺ
    27ÔćĺAnd as early as possible in your application, import and configure dotenv:
    28Ôćĺ
    29Ôćĺ```javascript
    30Ôćĺrequire('dotenv').config() // or import 'dotenv/config' if you're using ES6
    31Ôćĺ...
    32Ôćĺconsole.log(process.env) // remove this after you've confirmed it is working
    33Ôćĺ```
    34Ôćĺ
    35ÔćĺThat's it. `process.env` now has the keys and values you defined in your `.env` file:
    36Ôćĺ
    37Ôćĺ&nbsp;
    38Ôćĺ
    39Ôćĺ## Advanced
    41Ôćĺ<details><summary>ES6</summary><br>
    42Ôćĺ
    43ÔćĺImport with [ES6](#how-do-i-use-dotenv-with-import):
    44Ôćĺ
    45Ôćĺ```javascript
    46Ôćĺimport 'dotenv/config'
    47Ôćĺ```
    48Ôćĺ
    49ÔćĺES6 import if you need to set config options:
    50Ôćĺ
    51Ôćĺ```javascript
    52Ôćĺimport dotenv from 'dotenv'
    53Ôćĺdotenv.config({ path: '/custom/path/to/.env' })
    54Ôćĺ```
    55Ôćĺ
    56Ôćĺ</details>
    57Ôćĺ<details><summary>bun</summary><br>
    58Ôćĺ
    59Ôćĺ```sh
    60Ôćĺbun add dotenv
    61Ôćĺ```
    62Ôćĺ
    63Ôćĺ</details>
    64Ôćĺ<details><summary>yarn</summary><br>
    65Ôćĺ
    66Ôćĺ```sh
    67Ôćĺyarn add dotenv
    68Ôćĺ```
    69Ôćĺ
    70Ôćĺ</details>
    71Ôćĺ<details><summary>pnpm</summary><br>
    72Ôćĺ
    73Ôćĺ```sh
    74Ôćĺpnpm add dotenv
    75Ôćĺ```
    76Ôćĺ
